 writer's first version"},{"type":"text","text":"['maenjuskrxpt]"},{"type":"text","text":"of a book)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：manu（手）+script（写）→手稿"},{"type":"entry","text":"cowardice","headword":"cowardice"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 胆小,儒弱(fear or lack of courage)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kauardis]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：coward（胆小鬼）+ice（表性质）→胆小"},{"type":"entry","text":"shackle","headword":"shackle"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 束绑(to restrict, confine, or hamper)"},{"type":"text","text":"['{aekl]"},{"type":"text","text":"留 The uniquely human ability to rethink and revise our social arrangements is a"},{"type":"text","text":"se sn opyeus o Ajaxl se ane jeu swagsss ojeauo ol sn Sumoe fuissl piiam"},{"type":"text","text":"to liberate us."},{"type":"text","text":"trammel"}]},{"number":21,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"faction","headword":"faction"},{"type":"text","text":"(dno6 a6jel e uum jauo ugoe adoad jo dnob e) u"},{"type":"text","text":"[faek{n]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：fac（做）+tion→一帮人一起做→派系"},{"type":"entry","text":"inexpressible","headword":"inexpressible"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj难以言传的(impossible to express)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,nxk'spresabl]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：in（不）+expressible（可形容的）→不可形容的→难以言传的"},{"type":"entry","text":"mockery","headword":"mockery"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 笑(scornfully contemptuous ridicule; derision)"},{"type":"text","text":"['ma:kari]"},{"type":"text","text":"derision"},{"type":"entry","text":"ramification","headword":"ramification"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.结果，后果(consequence)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,raemrfr'ker[n]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自ramify（n.分支，分叉），引申词义“后果”，特指难以预料的结果。"},{"type":"entry","text":"underpin","headword":"underpin"},{"type":"text","text":"[Andar'prn]"},{"type":"text","text":"组合词：under（在下面）+pin(别针，固定）→在下面用别针再固定一下→加强"},{"type":"entry","text":"disregard","headword":"disregard"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 不