edlictable changeableness of mood)"},{"type":"text","text":"[m3:r'kjurial]"},{"type":"text","text":"volatile, inconstant"},{"type":"entry","text":"tactful","headword":"tactful"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj圆滑的：得体的，不得罪人的(considerate and discreet)"},{"type":"text","text":"['taktfl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：tact（得体）+ful(的）→得体"},{"type":"text","text":"diplomatic"},{"type":"text","text":"tactless（adj言行不得体的：得罪人的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"retroactive","headword":"retroactive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj (决定或行为)有追溯效力的(influencing or applying to a period prior to"},{"type":"text","text":"[retrau'aektiv]"},{"type":"text","text":"enactment)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：retro（向后，往回）+active（有效力的）→往回（追溯）有效力→有追潮效"},{"type":"text","text":"力的"},{"type":"text","text":"retroactively (adv 追潮地)"},{"type":"entry","text":"erroneous","headword":"erroneous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.错误的（not correct)"},{"type":"text","text":"[1'raunias]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：err(错误）+one+ous（的）→错误的"},{"type":"text","text":"inaccurate"},{"type":"entry","text":"purview","headword":"purview"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. (组织或活动的)范围，权限(the general scope and coverage of an organization"},{"type":"text","text":"['p3:rvju:]"},{"type":"text","text":"or activity)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：pur（穿过）+view（看）→在视线所及的范围之内→范围"},{"type":"entry","text":"immaterial","headword":"immaterial"},{"type":"text","text":"[ma'trrial]"},{"type":"text","text":"or form)"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：im（不）+material（物质的，重要的）→无形体的，不重要的"},{"type":"text","text":"inconsequential"},{"type":"entry","text":"unassailable","headword":"unassailable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不容置疑的(not liable to doubt, attack, or question)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Ana'serlabl]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：un（不）+assail（攻击）+able（可的）→不可攻击的→不可战胜的"},{"type":"text","text":"Although the claim that no one knows what dark matter is remains"},{"type":"text","text":"unassailable, some scientists dispute the parallel assertion that dark matter has"},{"type":"text","text":"not been detected."}]},{"number":27,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"maudlin","headword":"maudlin"},{"type":"text","text":"(aus Aawxae d-jis jo , ao ps Ajaisna) (pe"},{"type":"text","text":"[up:cu,]"},{"type":"text","text":"lachrymose, mawkish, mushy, overemotional, sentimental, tearful"},{"type":"entry","text":"largesse","headword":"largesse"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 慷低解囊(liberal giving (as of money) to or as if to an inferior);赠款(money or"},{"type":"text","text":"[la:r'd3es]"},{"type":"text","text":"gifts bestowed)"},{"type":"entry","text":"boorish","headword":"boorish"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj粗鲁讨厌的，粗野的(very unpleasant and rude)"},{"type":"text","text":"[bur]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自boor（n.粗鲁讨厌的人）"},{"type":"text","text":"churlish"},{"type":"entry","text":"quirky","headword":"quirky"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 古怪的(odd or unpredlictable in appearance, character, or behaviour)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kw3:rki]"},{"type":"text","text":"unconventional"},{"type":"entry","text":"antediluvian","headword":"antediluvian"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj陈旧的;过时的(old, old-fashioned);大洪水之前的(occurring or belonging"},{"type":"text","text":"[aentidr'lu:vian]"},{"type":"text","text":"to the era before the Flood)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：ante（在·之前）+diluvi（大洪水）+an(的）→大洪水之前的"},{"type":"text","text":"archaic"},{"type":"entry","text":"unruly","headword":"unruly"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.难以控制的，难以驾驭的（difficult to control or manage)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'ru:li]"},{"type":"text","text":"unruliness (n. 任性)"},{"type":"entry","text":"seizure","headword":"seizure"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 夺取, 占领(the act of using force to take control of a country, town, etc.)"},{"type":"text","text":"['si:3ar]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自seize（v夺取，占领）"},{"type":"entry","text":"conceal","headword":"conceal"},{"type":"definition","text":"v隐藏，掩盖（hide）"},{"type":"text"