根记忆：al（表加强）+luv（洗，冲洗）+ial→冲积的"},{"type":"entry","text":"detritus","headword":"detritus"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 残余物(disintegrated or eroded matter; debris)"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：de（向下）+trit（摩擦）+us→向下摩擦产生的物质→残余物"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'trartas]"},{"type":"text","text":"debris, residue"},{"type":"entry","text":"disgorge","headword":"disgorge"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.大量涌出，倾泻出(to pour something out in large quantities)"},{"type":"text","text":"[drs'g>:rd3]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：dis（分离）+gorg（喉）+e→与喉哦分离→呕出→大量涌出"},{"type":"text","text":"eject, belch"},{"type":"entry","text":"detached","headword":"detached"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 单独的(not joined to another house on either side)：冷漠的(indifferent);客"},{"type":"text","text":"[ae1,1p]"},{"type":"text","text":"(jeedw)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：de（表否定）+tach（钉）+ed→不钉在一起的→单独的"},{"type":"entry","text":"migratory","headword":"migratory"},{"type":"text","text":"(uogebw opouad busobepun uogebi Aq pazjaoeeuo)gn (pe"},{"type":"text","text":"['margrats:ri]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自migrate（v.迁徙）"}]},{"number":29,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"seditious","headword":"seditious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 始动性的(intended to encourage people to oppose a government)"},{"type":"text","text":"[s'dtfas]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：sed（坐）+it（走）+ious（·的）→让坐着的人走起来→编动性的"},{"type":"text","text":"agitational, instigative, provocative"},{"type":"entry","text":"magnify","headword":"magnify"},{"type":"text","text":"magnify"},{"type":"definition","text":"v放大（enlarge），扩大；增强；弯大"},{"type":"text","text":"['maegnrfar]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：magni（大）+fy（使）→放大"},{"type":"text","text":"magnificent (aoj. 壮丽的)"},{"type":"entry","text":"germane","headword":"germane"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj有密切关系的，恰当的（relevant)"},{"type":"text","text":"[d33:r'mein]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：germ（种子）+ane（的）→同种的→关系密切的"},{"type":"text","text":"apposite"},{"type":"en